	\'95	Restore Meaning: Reconnect modern translations with the physical realities behind ancient words.\
	\'95	Standardize Key Terms: Clarify essential biblical concepts (e.g., righteousness, spirit, wisdom).\
	\'95	Theologically Anchor: Prioritize Scripture interpreting Scripture.\
	\'95	Cross-Layer Revelation: Demonstrate linguistic unity across Torah, Prophets, Writings, and the New Testament.\
\
Why This Matters:\
Modern translations often obscure deep-rooted theological truths through over-abstraction. BLDP restores textual richness by focusing on word origins and physical meaning, drawing readers into covenantal depth.\
